@startuml
title voice-api - FastAPI 음성 합성 서비스 내부 구조

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<frontend>> {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}

actor "Frontend\n(Browser)" as FE <<frontend>>
component "Backend\n(토큰 검증 endpoint)" as BE <<external>>
component "Microsoft edge-tts\n(외부 TTS 서비스)" as Edge <<external>>

package "voice-api/" {
  component "main.py\n(FastAPI App + CORS + Lifespan)" as Main

  package "core" {
    component "config\n(Settings · env)" as Core_Cfg
    component "auth\n(Bearer JWT 검증 호출)" as Core_Auth
    component "logger\n(structlog)" as Core_Log
  }

  package "api" {
    component "routes/\n(POST /tts · POST /tts/stream\nGET /healthz)" as Routes
    component "schemas/\n(Pydantic Request · Response)" as Schemas
  }

  package "services" {
    component "TTSService\n(edge-tts wrapper +\nstreaming generator)" as TTSSvc
  }
}

FE --> Main : HTTPS Bearer JWT
Main --> Routes
Routes ..> Schemas : validate
Routes --> Core_Auth : require_user
Core_Auth --> BE : POST /verify
Routes --> TTSSvc : synthesize(text, voice)
TTSSvc --> Edge : Edge TTS WebSocket
TTSSvc --> Routes : audio/mpeg stream
Routes --> FE : mp3 chunk (Server-Sent stream)

Core_Cfg ..> Main
Core_Cfg ..> TTSSvc
Core_Log ..> Routes

footer voice-api/ — FastAPI · edge-tts · Bearer JWT 검증 · 스트리밍 응답
@enduml
